Package: flowcoind
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: FlowCoin daemon - RandomX CPU-only Proof-of-Work blockchain
 FlowCoin is a CPU-only Proof-of-Work cryptocurrency secured by
 RandomX, the memory-hard algorithm used by Monero. This package
 contains the full node daemon (flowcoind), the CLI client
 (flowcoin-cli), the offline transaction utility (flowcoin-tx),
 and the standalone CPU miner (flowcoin-miner).

Package: flowcoin-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: FlowCoin CLI - command line RPC client
 Lightweight command-line client for communicating with a running
 flowcoind instance via JSON-RPC. Does not include the full node
 daemon or wallet functionality.
